label day4_vanish_obo:

  me "Kanae, wait."

  show oyab surprised
  with dissolve

  show kanae_alt surprised
  with dissolve

  me "Put your hand in one of his foreheads"

  show kanae_alt normal
  with dissolve

  show oyab speaking soft
  with dissolve
  
  hide oyab speaking soft
  with dissolve

  show kanae_alt normal:
    xalign 0.3
  with move

  show obo happy at center
  with dissolve

  show kanae_alt speaking
  with dissolve

  kanae_alt """
  Now what?
  """

  show kanae_alt normal
  with dissolve

  me """
  Calm, Kanae

  Feel the time flowing as when we are preparing to jump into the void.

  Focus on nothing but him. See how each leaf is falling

  Each tree branch waving
  """

  show obo normal
  with dissolve

  show kanae_alt surprised
  with dissolve

  kanae_alt """
  I... I see it
  """

  hide kanae_alt surprised
  with dissolve

  play sound wind fadein 1.0 fadeout 1.0 loop

  """
  Both bodies enter a state of calm where they stop moving and simply feel the tranquility of their surroundings

  I try to visualize something different. They should feel that they lived more than this.
  """

  show obo happy
  with dissolve

  """
  I feel a faint breeze around them. It was accelerating, and so was the wrinkles on their skin
  """

  hide obo happy
  with Dissolve(5.0)

  """
  When we removed our hands, their bodies gradually became dust, while this happened our rings were marked in a subtle way by the lives we took. Had finished
  """

  stop sound fadeout 3.0

  show kanae_alt normal at left:
    xalign 0.2
  with dissolve

  show kanae_alt surprised
  with dissolve

  kanae_alt "I did not knew this."

  show kanae_alt normal
  with dissolve